arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
--Ograi speaks to hearing the Grinning One

local idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_OGAI_02) then
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_OGRAI_RITUAL_COMPLETE, idOwner, ID_OGAI_02)
end

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()
